 South Africa has recorded 521 318 confirmed infections, according to an announcement by the minister of health, Dr Zweli Mkhize, on Tuesday, August 4. A total of 15 693 of those cases have been reported in Mpumalanga. According to data released by the Mpumalanga Department of Health, there have been 10 736 recoveries and 123 deaths to date.  Click on the image for an enlarged view • Bushbuckridge: 389 cases, 303 recoveries and four deaths
